summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Textzy WhatsApp Business & SMS platform. All pages load correctly, navigation works seamlessly, and UI components display properly with mock data.
passed_tests: Landing page loads with hero section, features, pricing, testimonials, and footer
Login button navigation to /login page works correctly
Get Started button navigation to /register page works correctly
Login page renders with email/password fields and proper styling
Register page renders with all required fields including industry dropdown
Dashboard overview loads with stats cards and charts
All 11 sidebar navigation items are clickable and functional (Dashboard, Inbox, Contacts, Campaigns, Templates, Automations, Analytics, Integrations, Team, Billing, Settings, Admin)
Inbox page displays three-pane layout with conversations, chat area, and contact info
Contacts page navigation works (shows contact management interface)
Campaigns page shows campaign table with proper status badges
Templates page displays DLT Template IDs and approval statuses correctly
Automations page loads with automation management interface
Analytics page displays comprehensive charts and metrics
Integrations page shows API integration management
Billing page displays plan and usage information
Settings page loads with configuration options
Team page shows team member management
Admin page shows tenant management (super admin panel)
